  "detailed_description": "The game tells a story about a crazy skydiver, who decided that for an extreme jump with a parachute... he doesn't need a parachute. Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of air travel, avoid obstacles, dodge them, maneuver... Do everything to make the dream of the extreme - conquer the sky - come true!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dynamic gameplay<br></li><li> Gradually increasing complexity<br></li><li> Online leaderboard<br></li><li> Achievements system<br></li><li> Minimalistic graphics</li></ul>",
